INSERT INTO `comment` VALUES (16,108,'userpro',118,'He is most enthusiastic member in our Team ','','2015-05-30 18:03:24',' 108 144',''),(17,100,'ngopro',350,'Dnip Care is one of the few org which share their financial booklet publicly. Hats off to Dnipcare ','','2015-05-30 18:31:28',' 100 108',''),(15,108,'opp',95,'The internship is still open. You can mail your resume at helpiezteam@gmail.com. Thanks','','2015-05-30 17:30:07',' 108 160',''),(18,108,'ngopro',409,'test','info@pratham.org','2015-05-31 17:07:33',' 108',''),(19,108,'userpro',118,'and m very serious about my statement','','2015-05-31 17:10:29','',''),(22,752,'opp',93,'Hi,\r\nIs this internship still open?','helpiezteam@gmail.com','2015-06-04 21:10:59',' 752',''),(23,0,'opp',101,'applied','','2015-06-10 05:56:23','',''),(24,0,'opp',101,'','','2015-06-10 05:56:29','',''),(25,0,'opp',18,'nm mn','','2015-09-17 17:17:21','',''),(26,0,'opp',18,'The following time I learn a wloebg, I hope that it doesnt disappoint me as a lot as this one. I mean, I do know it was my option to read, however I actually thought youd have one thing interesting to say. All I hear is a bunch of whining about something that you might fix if you happen to werent too busy on the lookout for attention. regards!','','2015-09-19 06:14:07','',''),(27,0,'opp',101,'Sir,I am a serving govt eylpomee. I had applied for plastic card last year. My dispensary is Kali bari marg No 76. Our CMO who retired recently did not do his job properly because of that we are suffering for not getting the plastic card well in time. I had requested our doctors and also cghs helpline many number of times nobody helped me. Kindly let me know whom I should contact and what I should do in this poisition','','2015-09-19 11:18:38','',''),(28,0,'opp',86,'I heartily coemmnd you for this encouragement.  I am so tired of the hatred and conflict that has arisen ever since Obama was first elected in 2008.  What you have suggested is a recipe that should help all of us to get through these tough times if we will try it.  Through publishing these suggestions and this video, you have raised yourself up a notch in my book, and it is a breath of fresh air compared to many of the other publications that I read.','','2015-09-19 11:38:38','',''),(29,0,'opp',54,'Hi,I have got a query regarding gogole custom search engine.I am using gogole custom search engine in my website.I have disallowed gogole web search to crawl on some of my private pages through robots.txt.Will it also effect the gogole custom search engine I have used in my website?for example i have the below code in my robots.txt pageUser-agent: *Disallow: /usersAllow: /I hope this code will disallow the gogole web search to show the pages under users/. But Will it also disallow the gogole custom search engine to list out the results under users page.','','2015-09-19 12:33:39','',''),(30,0,'opp',65,'Ppl like you get all the brnasi. I just get to say thanks for he answer.','','2015-09-19 12:37:51','',''),(31,0,'opp',95,'Your posting really stiehgrtenad me out. Thanks!','','2015-09-19 14:42:40','',''),(32,0,'opp',93,'Emerging Jharkhand Times Impact Awards is initiative of adetnvisirg agencies of Ranchi and Event Management Companies who try to give a tribute those people who think, work and gathered information for Jharkhand and its people.','','2015-09-20 18:34:08','','');
