your&nbsp;volunteering&nbsp;and work alongside a team. This would give you a chance to contribute directly or indirectly towards impact. In addition, your experience would be invaluable in inculcating human skills necessary for building a satisfying career in the social space. During the six month&nbsp;volunteering, you would not be paid any salary. However, your travel and lodging costs related to your assignment, if any, would be reimbursed.','anywhere','','none',' Community Development','hr@drishtee.com','','Graduate/PG','6 months','04/01/2015','381 382 384 466','','','','2015-03-11 06:05:04','Project-Management','','','checked','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00',''),(66,'Financial Inclusion','internship',361,201,'2','<p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Overview :&nbsp;</span></p><p>The financial inclusion landscape in India is rapidly changing because of several reasons :</p><ul><li>Improved internet connectivity and extensive mobile penetration.</li><li><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">The increased interest on the part of the government to incorporate the hitherto financially&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">excluded into the banking system.</span></li><li><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">Implementation of the Adhaar Card â€“ a Unique Identification Card, with biometric identifiers and&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">the push to link bank accounts with the Adhaar identification.</span></li><li><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">The recent announcement by the Reserve Bank of India to issue licenses for special entities called&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">payment banks.&nbsp;</span></li></ul><p><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">For several years, Drishtee has been operating in the financial inclusion space and facilitates a network&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">of 1300 Customer Service Points for Indiaâ€™s largest Public Sector Bank â€“ the State Bank of India. Given&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">the changing landscape and the interest of new players into the segment, it must identify a strategy&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">built on increased operational efficiency and its deep understanding of rural India to survive and thrive,&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">while staying true to its vision to support sustainable communities in rural India.&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\">Task Description :</span></p><p>The Intern/Fellow will examine existing management and operational control systems and advice on one&nbsp;<span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">or more of the following:</span></p><ol><li><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">&nbsp;Build a technology strategy for Drishteeâ€™s Financial&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 24.5px;\">Inter-mediation</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">&nbsp;work. To develop the&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">technology strategy, the intern/fellow must examine Drishteeâ€™s current operations and&nbsp;</span><span style=\"line-height: 1.75;\">technology infrastructure.</span></li></ol>','Noida ','','none',' Disaster Management','hr@drishtee.com','','Graduate/PG','3 months','04/01/2015','','','','http://helpiez.org/img/volBackImg/66_20150314_110435.jpg','2015-03-11 06:08:20','Financial-Inclusion','','','checked','','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','','0000-00-00 00:00:00',''),(73,'Researching Reality Internship with Centre for Civil Society','internship',318,34,'Not Specified','<p><font face=\"arial, helvetica, sans-serif\" color=\"#000000\" style=\"font-size: 12.8000001907349px; line-height: normal;\">Researching Reality Internship is for college students and researchers who wish to apply social and economic principles to real-life problems through in-depth research projects. It provides interns with valuable training in areas of research, analysis, writing, and above all critical thinking. Interns study various agencies, boa