one & Google Hangout. It is not a training programme. you will not be teached how to makethe designs we only provide you what we require, it is upto you how you make it?','Virtual','','No stipend. Only Out of Pocket Expenses shall be reimbursed',' Children & Youth, Education & Employment, Health & Medicine','savethegirlngo@gmail.com',' Multimedia & Designing','Having Good Knowledge of Multimedia','2  months','26/05/15','671 744','671 ','','./img/cause/internbanner.jpg','2015-04-26 10:12:42','Internship-in-Multimedia,-Poster-Designing','','','checked','','2015-06-01 07:00:00',' Virtual','yes','0000-00-00 00:00:00','East Delhi'),(90,'Operation /Marketing / content','internship',108,367,'15 each ','<p><strong>Operation</strong> - We need responsible and intuitive individuals who can help us expand amongst the NGOs. You would have to contact NGOs for extracting social opportunities from them and would have to follow up with them throughout the duration of internship. &nbsp;</p>\r\n<p><strong>Market survey &amp; Social campaign</strong> - Your work is to develop creative slogans, interact with people of Delhi to motivate them for volunteering and conduct various survey for this market.</p>\r\n<p><strong>Content Development </strong> - We need thoughtful people who can very well articulate their thoughts in a beautifully written piece of article on social issues prevailing in our societies(It will include ground research and market survey). They would also have to publicize it in the various social media and also do SEO of it.</p>','New Delhi, Delhi, India','','Reimbursed',' Community Development','helpiezteam@gmail.com',' Creative content writing, Multimedia & Designing, Strategy & Analytics, Community Engagement, Marketing & Publicity, Operation & Logistics',' An inquisitive nature would be encouraged, irrespective of your CGPA and previous experience.','50 Days','19-05-2015','661 662 667 668 675 677 680 433 673','673 433 680 677 675 667 662 661 668 ','','./img/cause/in