-family: Calibri; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">â— &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Supporting the Fellow in the</span> <span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">classroom are from 07:30 Hrs to 14:00 Hrs.</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">â— &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Supporting school relations</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: normal; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">â— &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Reporting to the Teach For India Delhi team on a weekly basis.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong id=\"docs-internal-guid-8b93bb78-6b10-fd01-c4bf-ae2c8715088d\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">&nbsp;</strong></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px; font-family: Calibri; color: #000000; background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; text-decoration: none; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;\">Knowledge, Skills and Abilities:</span></p>\r\n<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height: 1.3800000000000001; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 10pt;